headline: Is Carnival Stock Still Sailing Below Its True Worth After Strong 40.6% Jump?
summary: If you’re watching Carnival Corporation & stock and wondering whether it’s a buy or a sell, you’re not alone. It’s been an exciting cruise for shareholders, and deciding what to do next can feel as complex as steering a ship into a busy port. The stock has delivered an impressive 40.6% gain over the past year. That’s not even the whole story; if you zoom out to the past three years, it’s up a staggering 228.9%.
